00:17:25.879 --> 00:17:27.505
These sons of bitches
are so far up my ass.

244
00:17:27.589 --> 00:17:28.673
they're staring at the back
of my tonsils.

245
00:17:28.757 --> 00:17:30.216
Well. it's gonna have to be tomorrow.

246
00:17:30.759 --> 00:17:32.135
'cause I think I found our plane.

247
00:17:33.928 --> 00:17:35.221
You guys lost a plane?

248
00:17:35.972 --> 00:17:38.057
