but since you're not.

282
00:19:09.566 --> 00:19:10.859
I called the airplane police.

283
00:19:10.942 --> 00:19:13.486
- It's their job to call you. not mine.
- Well. they didn't.

284
00:19:13.570 --> 00:19:16.030
Well. I don't know what to tell you.
That's the federal government for you.

285
00:19:16.823 --> 00:19:18.324
What's all this?

286
00:19:18.408 --> 00:19:20.827
WALT: One of 75 reasons
you should have called me

287
00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:22.620
