288
00:19:22.704 --> 00:19:24.372
- Cocaine?
- Maybe.

289
00:19:24.956 --> 00:19:26.165
Maybe heroin.

290
00:19:26.249 --> 00:19:27.458
Where's the pilot?

291
00:19:27.542 --> 00:19:28.710
Cooking in the cockpit.

292
00:19:29.836 --> 00:19:34.132
I got DEA and FAA sending HAZMAT crews
down here to pull him out.

293
00:19:35.508 --> 00:19:38.511
Stay upwind of that shit.
It'll kill you quicker than a bullet.

294
00:19:39.095 --> 00:19:40.388
That's a TTP truck.

295
00:19:41.097 --> 00:19:42.181
Yep.

296
00:19:42.265 --> 00:19:43.474
