302
00:19:56.237 --> 00:19:58.948
And then a couple months later.
they find their way back.

303
00:19:59.449 --> 00:20:01.492
If I reported everything
that was stolen around here.

304
00:20:01.576 --> 00:20:03.953
the whole fucking Permian Basin
would be a crime scene.

305
00:20:05.330 --> 00:20:06.539
God damn it.

306
00:20:06.623 --> 00:20:09.959
I got 4.200 barrels of oil
I got to move out of here every day.

307
00:20:10.043 --> 00:20:12.712
Not on this road. Not for a while.

308
00:20:12.795 --> 00:20:14.631
I'm gonna need some love
on this deal. Walt.

309
00:20:15.298 --> 00:20:16.466
What kind of love?

310
