The kind that backdates
a police report.

311
00:20:19.218 --> 00:20:20.762
For God sakes. Tommy.

312
00:20:20.845 --> 00:20:23.514
The FAA was aware.
They dropped the ball.

313
00:20:23.598 --> 00:20:25.725
Just use the date that I gave them.

314
00:20:25.808 --> 00:20:27.352
and match it. that's all.

315
00:20:27.435 --> 00:20:29.687
You know how many eyes
are gonna be on this thing?

316
00:20:29.771 --> 00:20:31.773
The kind with a "G"
on their license plate.

317
00:20:32.732 --> 00:20:33.900
I ain't backdating nothing.

318
00:20:33.983 --> 00:20:36.361
Okay. in today's report.

319
