just note that FAA
was notified last month.

320
00:20:40.490 --> 00:20:41.699
Can you do that?

321
00:20:43.451 --> 00:20:45.328
It's the fucking truth. Walt.

322
00:20:46.746 --> 00:20:47.997
I'll put it in my report.

323
