and the drugs are? No.

331
00:21:09.894 --> 00:21:11.771
Okay. well. how about
that side over there?

332
00:21:11.854 --> 00:21:13.690
Is there any dead bodies
and dope over there?

333
00:21:13.773 --> 00:21:14.983
WALT: Haven't looked over there yet.

334
00:21:15.066 --> 00:21:17.527
TOMMY: Well. how about
we fucking go look then? Shit.

335
00:21:23.866 --> 00:21:26.369
Well. I don't see
any dead drug dealers over here.

336
00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:29.038
Not any dead guys here.
not any dope…

337
00:21:30.039 --> 00:21:31.082
Fuck.

338
00:21:31.165 --> 00:21:32.250
(INSECTS BUZZING)

339
00:21:33.167 --> 00:21:34.210
Walt?

340
00:21:34.293 --> 00:21:36.254
There's a dead son of a bitch
