397
00:24:02.191 --> 00:24:03.401
<i>Do you like it?</i>

398
00:24:03.484 --> 00:24:04.944
Yes. I do like it.

399
00:24:05.027 --> 00:24:07.697
<i>You see. one of life's great pleasures</i>

400
00:24:07.780 --> 00:24:10.116
<i>is showing you what you're missing.</i>

401
00:24:10.199 --> 00:24:11.951
You don't have to show me
