402
00:24:12.034 --> 00:24:13.035
I already know.

403
00:24:13.703 --> 00:24:14.829
<i>How's our baby?</i>

404
00:24:15.705 --> 00:24:17.248
Uh. it's his first day.

405
00:24:17.331 --> 00:24:18.708
First days ain't easy.

406
00:24:18.791 --> 00:24:20.668
<i>Another Norris in the oil patch.</i>

407
00:24:21.627 --> 00:24:22.628
<i>What a waste.</i>

408
00:24:22.712 --> 00:24:23.963
Wasn't my idea.

409
00:24:24.046 --> 00:24:25.965
<i>Apple don't fall far. does it?</i>

410
00:24:26.048 --> 00:24:29.093
