415
00:24:47.195 --> 00:24:48.988
MAN: <i>The way I got started in this.</i>

416
00:24:49.071 --> 00:24:52.867
<i>I was working in West Texas
as a petroleum engineer</i>

417
00:24:53.826 --> 00:24:56.454
<i>and I decided that it was time</i>

418
00:24:56.537 --> 00:24:59.373
<i>to have a little adventure in life.</i>

419
00:25:00.666 --> 00:25:03.753
<i>And I answered
this one particular advertisement</i>

420
00:25:03.836 --> 00:25:06.088
<i>to go to work for a company in Libya</i>

421
00:25:06.672 --> 00:25:08.382
