422
00:25:09.008 --> 00:25:11.093
<i>My Arabic friends used to laugh at me</i>

423
00:25:11.177 --> 00:25:13.971
<i>because I would speak Arabic
with a Texas accent.</i>

424
00:25:14.472 --> 00:25:18.017
And it was hard for them
to understand my Arabic.

425
00:25:18.100 --> 00:25:19.810
even though I was
speaking the true words.

426
00:25:20.686 --> 00:25:24.315
Things were going along
pretty well until 1967.

427
00:25:24.398 --> 00:25:26.150
There was the Arab/Israeli War.

428
00:25:26.234 --> 00:25:29.695
And we could certainly see
that the Arab view

429
00:25:29.779 --> 00:25:34.450
