was beginning to dim.

430
00:25:34.951 --> 00:25:35.993
CHUBBY: I will tell you what.

431
00:25:36.077 --> 00:25:38.621
I am about done
with looking north of I-20.

432
00:25:39.288 --> 00:25:42.041
I sunk three wells last week.
I didn't even hit water.

433
00:25:42.124 --> 00:25:44.168
It's because there ain't
any water north of I-20.

434
00:25:44.252 --> 00:25:45.461
More than there is south of it.

435
00:25:45.544 --> 00:25:47.505
- MONTY: What county?
- Stonewall.

436
00:25:47.588 --> 00:25:49.382
Shit. they been sucking that oil
for a hundred years.

437
00:25:49.465 --> 00:25:52.093
Frack the ones that are going dry
and get the hell out.

438
00:25:52.176 --> 00:25:53.844
Besides. what are you
gonna do with three wells?

439
00:25:53.928 --> 00:25:56.055
- (PHONE BUZZING)
- That's where my minerals are.

440
00:25:56.138 --> 00:25:57.181
(CHUCKLES)

441
00:25:57.765 --> 00:26:00.059
