444
00:26:05.606 --> 00:26:07.191
That ain't big. that's smart.

445
00:26:07.275 --> 00:26:11.028
There ain't no new oil to be
found in that rocky red dirt.

446
00:26:11.112 --> 00:26:13.656
- (PHONE BUZZING)
- Shit. This ain't gonna be good.

447
00:26:13.739 --> 00:26:14.824
Give me a second. boys.

448
00:26:14.907 --> 00:26:16.325
CHUBBY: Yeah. go ahead. Monty.

449
00:26:16.951 --> 00:26:18.327
Hey. let me get somewhere quiet.

450
00:26:20.162 --> 00:26:21.580
(SOFT DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING)

451
00:26:23.541 --> 00:26:24.750
All right. how bad?

452
00:26:24.834 --> 00:26:26.502
TOMMY: <i>That's a tricky one to answer.</i>

453
00:26:26.585 --> 00:26:28.254
