454
00:26:28.337 --> 00:26:30.214
<i>Well. they're gonna hit you
from three directions.</i>

455
00:26:30.298 --> 00:26:33.509
The insurance company.
victims' families and TTP.

456
00:26:33.592 --> 00:26:34.760
All right. well. I'll handle TTP.

457
00:26:34.844 --> 00:26:36.595
Who's the best litigation firm
in Midland?

458
00:26:36.679 --> 00:26:38.597
<i>Well. they won't file here.
they'll file in Houston.</i>

459
00:26:38.681 --> 00:26:40.641
First one
to hire Shepherd-Hastings wins.

460
00:26:41.267 --> 00:26:42.601
Who do you like over there?

461
00:26:42.685 --> 00:26:45.104
Clay Chandler is an assassin.
You want me to call him?

462
00:26:45.187 --> 00:26:47.648
No. I'll call him. You just keep
this shit out of the news.

463
00:26:48.107 --> 00:26:50.276
TOMMY: (LAUGHS)
<i>This is the patch. Monty.</i>

464
00:26:50.985 --> 00:26:52.111
An airplane full of drugs

465
00:26:52.194 --> 00:26:54.113
being run over by an oil tanker
ain't news.

466
00:26:54.196 --> 00:26:55.573
that's just another Monday.

467
00:26:55.656 --> 00:26:57.408
Yeah. well. it ain't Monday. Tommy.

468
00:26:58.075 --> 00:26:59.368
<i>It's Monday to me.</i>

469
00:27:11.881 --> 00:27:13.299
(COOPER MOANS NERVOUSLY)

470
00:27:15.551 --> 00:27:17.219
(GRUNTING)

471
00:27:19.138 --> 00:27:20.681
(PANTING)

472
00:27:21.599 --> 00:27:22.933
What's he supposed to be checking?

473
00:27:24.060 --> 00:27:25.102
Tucker valve.

474
00:27:25.686 --> 00:27:27.021
What the fuck is a Tucker valve?

475
00:27:27.646 --> 00:27:28.898
First day on the job.

476
00:27:29.732 --> 00:27:32.151
Motherfucker. I can't have
Tommy Norris' son

477
00:27:32.234 --> 00:27:34.153
dying on my pad.
Get him down from there.

478
00:27:34.236 --> 00:27:35.404
All right. I'll do it right now.

479
00:27:35.988 --> 00:27:37.740
You got to go right up at the top!

480
00:27:37.823 --> 00:27:39.742
Like that? (CHUCKLING)

481
00:27:41.035 --> 00:27:42.078
